OL,3,CTaxes, Farms, and Scandals: The North
OL,4,CWest reacts to the Labour budget
OL,6,FITV News' Lise McNally got the
OL,7,Freaction of those affected by the
OL,8,Fbudget.
OL,10,FAs the dust settles on the first
OL,11,FLabour budget in almost 15 years,
OL,12,Fthose affected by its announcements
OL,13,Fhave shared their reaction, hopes, and
OL,14,Fworries for the future.
