OL,3,CTaxes, Farms, and Scandals: The North
OL,4,CWest reacts to the Labour budget
OL,6,FThe government hopes the historic
OL,7,FBudget - Labour's first since 2010 and
OL,8,Fthe first delivered by a female
OL,9,Fchancellor - will convince the public
OL,10,Fthat it can "rebuild Britain" and
OL,11,Frestore its creaking public services,
OL,12,Fwith pledges to "invest, invest,
OL,13,Finvest".
OL,15,FThe plans included support for those
OL,16,Fon low incomes with a rise in the
OL,17,Fminimum wage, as well as a #22.6
OL,18,Fbillion increase in the day-to-day NHS
OL,19,Fhealth budget.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/19
