OL,6,FThe Government also doubled down on
OL,7,Ftheir promise to provide compensation
OL,8,Fto victims of the infected blood
OL,9,Fscandal.
OL,11,FHowever, these historic policies came
OL,12,Fwith increases to national insurance
OL,13,Femployer contributions as well as cuts
OL,14,Fto agricultural property relief, which
OL,15,Fwill make farmland subject to
OL,16,Finheritance tax when it is passed from
OL,17,Fone generation to another.
