OL,3,CTaxes, Farms, and Scandals: The North
OL,4,CWest reacts to the Labour budget
OL,6,FAs people in the North West come to
OL,7,Fterms with what Labour's budget means
OL,8,Ffor them, we spoke to those affected
OL,9,Fby Rachel Reeves' decisions.
OL,11,FRachel Reeves announced an increase to
OL,12,Fnational insurance employer
OL,13,Fcontributions by 1.2 percentage points
OL,14,Fto 15%, which will come into effect
OL,15,Ffrom April 2025.
OL,17,FShe also lowered the Secondary
OL,18,FThreshold, the level at which
OL,19,Femployers start paying national
OL,20,Finsurance on each employee's salary,
OL,21,Ffrom #9,100 per year down to #5,000.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/19
