OL,6,F"I know that this is a difficult
OL,7,Fchoice. I do not take this decision
OL,8,Flightly," she said, pointing out that
OL,9,Fthis will raise a huge #25 billion per
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FWatching the announcement was Martin
OL,13,FTaylor, the owner and Director of
OL,14,FSandbar Seafood Shack, a restaurant in
OL,15,FChester Market.
OL,17,FHe said: "As a businessperson it's
OL,18,Fhard to be optimistic, especially
OL,19,Fafter the last few years we've had to
OL,20,Fendure."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/19
