OL,6,FMartin says that business was already
OL,7,Ftight before the budget, and now an
OL,8,Fincrease in prices is inevitable.
OL,10,FHe says: "Ultimately we're going to
OL,11,Fhave to put prices up across the
OL,12,Fboard. There's many businesses here
OL,13,Fand we're all working on almost
OL,14,Fidentical business models. We're all
OL,15,Fin agreement that sell prices will
OL,16,Fhave to go up to pay for that
OL,17,Foverhead."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/19
