OL,6,FWhile Martin was pleased to see the
OL,7,Fmoney would go towards further
OL,8,Fhealthcare funding, but worries
OL,9,Fsmaller businesses are paying the
OL,10,Fprice.
OL,12,FHe said: "My partner works in the NHS
OL,13,Fand it really needs that money. I do
OL,14,Ffeel that it could have been tiered so
OL,15,Flarge businesses are paying this rise,
OL,16,Fand then smaller business could stay
OL,17,Fon the flat rate so we can expand and
OL,18,Freach those heights."
