OL,6,FOne of the most unexpected
OL,7,Fannouncements from Rachel Reeves'
OL,8,Fbudget was the cuts to agricultural
OL,9,Fproperty relief. Under the new rules,
OL,10,Ffarming families will be able to pass
OL,11,Fup to #1m worth without any tax, but
OL,12,Fafter that 50% of the remaining value
OL,13,Fwill be eligible for taxation.
OL,15,FThe Chancellor said that the #1
OL,16,Fmillion band would help protect small
OL,17,Ffarms.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/19
