OL,6,FHowever, farmers say the threshold is
OL,7,Funlikely to be enough to protect even
OL,8,Fthe smallest of farms, meaning that
OL,9,Fpractically all farmers can now expect
OL,10,Fto be subject to inheritance tax (IHT)
OL,11,Fon their deaths.
OL,13,FThis opinion was shared by David Hall,
OL,14,Fwho has been in charge of Cherry
OL,15,FClough Farm in Oldham since his father
OL,16,Fdied when David was 16.
OL,18,FHe said: "I've been farming all my
OL,19,Flife. I've lived here all my life. We
OL,20,Ffarm just over 150 sheep and I just
OL,21,Freally enjoy it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/19
