OL,6,FNow that he has his own children,
OL,7,FDavid worries what the changes means
OL,8,Ffor them.
OL,10,FHe said: "I want to allow my children
OL,11,Fto do what I do if they want to follow
OL,12,Fin my footsteps but this will put a
OL,13,Fsignificant burden on any
OL,14,Fopportunities to pass the farm on.
OL,16,F"The farming community feels really
OL,17,Flet down by the Government."
OL,19,FDavid now hopes the Government will
OL,20,Fwork with farmers to make a policy
OL,21,Fthat better support independent farms.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/19
