OL,6,FHe said: "There is real concern in
OL,7,Fterms of the limit being put on the
OL,8,Ftax relief on land. We need to work
OL,9,Fwith the Government to make the scheme
OL,10,Fmore realistic, because right now it
OL,11,Fdoesn't feel fit for purpose."
OL,13,FDavid feels confident the new rules
OL,14,Fwill be changed to better suit family
OL,15,Ffarms, either by this Government or
OL,16,Fthe next one.
OL,18,FUntil then, David has no plans to
OL,19,Fretire or pass on the farm any time
OL,20,Fsoon.
