OL,3,CTaxes, Farms, and Scandals: The North
OL,4,CWest reacts to the Labour budget
OL,6,FIn the budget, Rachel Reeves announced
OL,7,Fthat victims of the infected blood and
OL,8,FHorizon scandals will receive
OL,9,Fcompensation in full, with #11.8
OL,10,Fbillion for all "infected and
OL,11,Faffected" by contaminated blood,
OL,12,Falongside #1.8 billion for victims of
OL,13,Fthe Post Office scandal.
OL,15,FThe news was relief for Gareth
OL,16,FMossman, who's father spent his life
OL,17,Ffighting for justice for the victims
OL,18,Fof the infected blood scandal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/19
