OL,6,FGareth said: "There's mixed emotions
OL,7,Fwith it. First of all, it's brilliant
OL,8,Fthey've committed t compensation and
OL,9,Fcommitted to a figure. That's really
OL,10,Fpositive and we've got to be happy
OL,11,Fabout that.
OL,13,F"I am a bit confused by the exact
OL,14,Ffigure of #11.8 billion. How can they
OL,15,Fput such an exact figure on it?"
OL,17,FThe average package is expected to be
OL,18,Faround #100,000 but some are set to
OL,19,Freceive much more.
